		    in
		        Output,
		        fx_Type = type function
		        (
		            p_Table as table
		            , p_DateFieldName as text
		        ) as table meta
		        [
		            Documentation.Name = "fx_GetYearIndex"
		            , Documentation.Description = "This function takes a table and date field name and returns a predictable index unique to the year that the date belongs to."
		            , Documentation.Examples = 
		            {
		                [
		                    Description = "Example usage of fx_CreateDimQuarter"
		                    , Code = "fx_GetYearIndex(#""FactInternetSales"", ""OrderDate"")"
		                    , Result = "2022"
		                ]
		            }
		        ]
		in
		Value.ReplaceType(fx, fx_Type)
		in
		    Source
		```
